	<Title>
		Cardiac asthma: What causes it?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Cardiac asthma refers to wheezing that&apos;s a sign of heart failure.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		What is cardiac asthma?
	</Question>
